## 6) After-Coding Checklist
- [ ] `CHANGELOG.md` updated
- [ ] Structure map section updated (if changed)
- [ ] Commands section updated (if changed)
- [ ] Matrix row(s) updated for new workflows
- [ ] AI context regenerated (`[AI_CONTEXT_COMMAND]`)
- [ ] Verify gate passed

## 7) Refactor Triggers and Workflow
- Trigger refactor if any source file exceeds 500 lines.
- Target <= 400 lines for new files.
- Extract cohesive modules without changing behavior.
- Re-run smoke + targeted tests + verify gate.
